        <updateDate>2003-09-25T18:48:27Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Quit Smoking Incentive and Opportunity Act of 2003 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a limited credit for the qualified tobacco use cessation expenses (approved cessation products and counseling) of a taxpayer, the taxpayer's spouse, or any dependent of the taxpayer.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
